  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study the investigators will study two dosages of heparin before extracorporeal
      circulation in open chest cardiac surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this study the investigators will study two dosages of heparin before extracorporeal
      circulation in open chest cardiac surgery. The first dosage will be 300 IU per kilogram of
      REAL weight, the second dosage will be 300 IU per kilogram of IDEAL weight.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
